headline: 2 No-Brainer Energy Stocks to Buy to Cash in on the Coming Power Surge
summary: The U.S. power sector is at an inflection point.  After barely growing over the last 20 years, electricity demand in the country is on track to surge over the next two decades.  Few companies are in a better position to capitalize on the expected surge in U.S. power demand than NextEra Energy (NYSE: NEE) and Brookfield Renewable (NYSE: BEPC)(NYSE: BEP).
